<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="guard-n">guard <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡɑːd/    美 /ɡɑːrd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>卫兵 (队)；警卫员；看守员；(篮球等的) 后卫：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>security guard</strong>
安全警卫/保安人员</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>point guard</strong>
控球后卫</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>守卫；警戒；看守：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>under</strong> heavy <strong>guard</strong>
在严密的看管下</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-guard">on guard</h3>
<p>1.<strong>站岗；值班：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The soldier was on guard all night.
士兵整夜站岗。</p></div>

<h3 id="off-sbs-guard">off (sb's) guard</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不提防；丧失警惕：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He struck me while I was off guard.
他趁我不备打了我。</p></div></div>